OL,3,CMum-of-three judged over hidden
OL,4,Cdisability
OL,6,FA mum-of-three from Beverley has
OL,7,Fspoken about receiving verbal abuse in
OL,8,Fpublic because of a hidden disability.
OL,10,FJenna Robinson has a bowl condition
OL,11,Fcalled slow transit constipation that
OL,12,Frequires her to wear a stoma bag over
OL,13,Fan opening in her abdomen.
OL,15,FAfter a C-section, she says it took
OL,16,Fher nine years to get properly
OL,17,Fdiagnosed and her struggle continues
OL,18,Fas people frequently judge her for
OL,19,Fusing disabled toilets.
