OL,6,FSpeaking to ITV News Calendar, she
OL,7,Fsaid: "It's really difficult to get
OL,8,Fthat courage to go out and then when I
OL,9,Fdo, I'm faced with 'You don't look
OL,10,Fdisabled, what are you in there for?'
OL,11,FIt does put me off from being out.
OL,13,F"It upsets me a lot if I'm honest,
OL,14,Fbecause I'm normally with my children.
OL,16,F"I've had a lady contact me who has
OL,17,Fbowel cancer, and she's not got a
OL,18,Fstoma, and she's been verbally abused
OL,19,Ffor just using the disabled toilet.
