OL,6,F"Just because somebody does not look
OL,7,Fdisabled, doesn't mean there's not
OL,8,Fanything going on underneath the
OL,9,Fclothes."
OL,11,FA study from charity Colostomy UK
OL,12,Ffound 62% of people felt that a lack
OL,13,Fof suitable toilet facilities were
OL,14,Fimpacting their day-to-day life.
OL,16,FIt also revealed 25% of people living
OL,17,Fwith a stoma have said they've been
OL,18,Fverbally or physically abused in the
OL,19,Fpast for using an accessible toilet,
OL,20,Fbecause they don't look visibly like
OL,21,Fthey need to use one.
