OL,6,FJenna is now campaigning with
OL,7,FColostomy UK for more accessible
OL,8,Ftoilets that include a hook, mirror,
OL,9,Fshelf and a sticker that says 'Stoma
OL,10,FFriendly'.
OL,12,FShe said: "I've had to go into a
OL,13,Fdisabled toilet and put medical
OL,14,Fsupplies on the dirty floor.... when
OL,15,Fwe have to plan our days out to a T.
OL,16,FIt's quite nice to be able to have a
OL,17,Ftoilet with everything that we need in
OL,18,Fthere."
